snippet.title: Turnabout Reality [FT] Just Phoenix.
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Playthrough]

A DDLC x Ace Attorney crossover case? You've got me interested.

Honestly, not too much to say about it other than... It's a good bit of charming fun! What happens? Tune in and see! Just some normal courtroom action!

......I am curious to see what more you could do with the meta aspect here if you ever feel like giving it a deeper dive~
-----------------------------------------
Turnabout Reality, by DJJ6800!

Phoenix Wright must defend a man accused of assaulting his daughter in front of school grounds. Facing off against an unfamiliar prosecutor, Phoenix discovers that things aren't exactly as they seem in this case. Or in this world, for that matter.

Made for the "Looking Back" Comp hosted by Super legenda and risefromtheashes. Won second place in that comp!

Find it on AA Online here: http://www.aaonline.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?p=778231&hilit=turnabout+reality#p778231
